data.revised_prompt: A tender moment in the sea, depicting a delightful baby sea otter. The otter is floating on its back, its short, glossy fur slightly wet. Its round, black eyes are radiating immense cuteness. Tufted ears and webbed paws add to its adorable appeal, which is set against the backdrop of an expansive turquoise sea with light, playful waves gently bobbing it above and below the water surface.
